Bash script: create a menu for user, for selecting different types of filters
Filter: set protocol field, fore example, MAC address, parse packages and find
those that contain same values, the output is names of those packages

bash script filter:

1) menus and submneus

2) grep patterns for filtering

3) parse all packages for chosen filtering in submenu

4) add those packages to global list

5) out from menu, printf this package list

!!! Add filtering current protocol fields using regex or += - check both


